-- Purpose: Centralizes MarketplaceService.ProcessReceipt with IDEMPOTENCY, GIFTING, VFX, and Anti-Exploit guards.
-- Runs on: Server
-- Location: ServerScriptService
-- Dependencies: MarketplaceService, DataStoreService, Players, Workspace, ServerStorage, ReplicatedStorage, HttpService
-- Public API: N/A
-- Networking: Listens to ProcessReceipt. Fires 'NotifyGiftReceived' to clients when gifted.
-- Security: Verifies target doesn't already own the item before granting to prevent wasted Robux via exploits.
-- Performance: Uses caching and pcalls for DataStore resilience.
-- Notes: Updated to support UNCOMMON SHOP tier purchases and rerolls.

